---
title: All-American Crumbed Chicken Burger with Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: You've been dreaming of an All-American flavoured crumbed chicken burger? Well how about that – so have we! And we promise you, with a crispy panko coating, creamy garlic aioli and oven-baked fries, it tastes even better in real life than we had imagined.

